imdb.plot outline: Rama is a middle class housewife living with her husband Abhay and two kids Arya and Nakul.On the night of eclipse Rama goes out to purchase ice cream for her family where she escapes a narrow accident after a bus passes by from her.Upon returning Rama is shocked to see that things have changed her house is missing and a building is come up on the same place. She roams on the street searching for her husband and kids.Niranjan who lives in the building where Rama's house resided comes to her aid thinking she must have lost her way in the dark.Rama provides him details of her family and her neighbor Mr Wagh.Niranjan tells her that he is been living here for 37 years and knows most people around and such people never existed here.As its too late Niranjan takes Rama to his house against wishes of his mother who feels Rama is either insane or a spirit roaming during the eclipse.
